      <div class="cd-tabs__nav">
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="1">Compatibility<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="2">Scalability<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="3">Security<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
        <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="4">User-Friendly Interface<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="5">Cost-Effectiveness<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
      </div>
      <div class="cd-tabs__content">
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="1">
          <p>Compatibility is at the heart of every successful POS integration. Our solutions are designed to work seamlessly with a wide variety of hardware, software, and third-party platforms, including inventory management, accounting, CRM, and e-commerce systems. We carefully evaluate your existing technology stack before recommending an integration path.</p>
          <p>By ensuring strong compatibility across systems, we eliminate data silos and reduce the risk of disruptions during the transition. This approach allows your business to continue operating smoothly while gaining the benefits of a fully connected POS environment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="2">
          <p>As your business grows, your POS system needs to grow with it. We build integrations that are designed with scalability in mind, allowing you to add new locations, sales channels, and applications without costly rework or downtime.</p>
          <p>Our scalable architecture ensures that increased transaction volumes, additional staff, and expanding product catalogs can be handled efficiently, so your POS system remains a reliable foundation as your operations expand.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="3">
